channel.title: Deemed [fullscreen]
channel.description:
hey, after releasing my client i thought that ide make a fullscreen client. out of my old base. what i aim to do is to have a proper fullscreen client and a small screen 1. with the option to choose both =].
this has been going well, but had some bad times. i just like to say major thanks to stewie and swat =]. this is my 1st attempt at something proper client side. so this is basically my 1st proper time doing client coding =]
so here is what i have done _____________ 28th july, 12:26pm _________ minimap (80%) - made minimap a circle (100%) - positioned minimap in correct place (95%)
_____________ 28th july, 13:43pm _________ minimap (90%) - positioned my orbs (0%)
_____________ 28th july, 16:32pm _________ tab area(10%) - positioned tabs(100%) - positioned hovered tabs(100%) - positioned clicked tabs(100%) - positioned tab icons(100%) - set inventary (100%)
_____________ 28th july, 22:03pm _________ chat area(60%) - positioned chat(100%) - positioned username(100%) - positioned entered text(100%) - positioned sent text(100%) - positioned sent name(100%)
_______________Media___________________ [SPOILER="Media"] [IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/20hr5op.png[/img] [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/2cp49zn.png[/img] [IMG]http://i30.tinypic.com/2m2x3ea.png[/img] [IMG]http://i31.tinypic.com/33571xy.png[/img] [IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/2rff2w0.png[/img] [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/hvats5.png[/img] [/SPOILER] _______________________________________
